summary: SERIE: HOW TO HAVE FUN “ What Plush Do You Want?” - 20/27 Yeah, you know... this drawing is okay. It's beautiful, it's colorful...
caption:
SERIE: HOW TO HAVE FUN

“ What Plush Do You Want?” - 20/27

Yeah, you know… this drawing is okay. It’s beautiful, it’s colorful … but I don’t like it. It’s the same scene as Rudy and Sunny, and it’s not what I wanted.
I wanted them to play, and I failed to do the pose, now it looks like they’re judging Fuyuki.

Isa saved my drawing with her beauty … LOOK AT HER! SHE IS SO FUCKING BEAUTIFUL!

Also Fuyuki is not shy this time

same place of Sis and her group, but in different time.
